<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tang hawihtak mai a um, gam gamla tak mai ah,
 Tuipi khel gam nuomtak mai a chun;
 A min &quot;Luguh mun&quot; ah Lalpa chuh a thi tai,
 Kei leh nang leh khawvel ding ahi.

[V2]
 A thawkdan ka hetin ka mitthi a luong hi,
 Zie tang chuh ka en bangtik inle;
 A sik a chun Isu'n A thuoka a thi tai;
 Kei guola gilo ngaihdamna di'n.

[V3]
 2. Lungkhamin A chieh hi kross giktak pu kawmin,
 Ling lukhuk kiphek chuh khu kawmin;
 Kross ah a khenden ui, mipi'n a nuihsan ui,
 Tang hawihtak a chun a khaikang ui.

[V4]
 3. A lungdawn zie ka hei, Amah a kan lai un,
 Hukdampa thingah a khenden ui;
 A Kross chuh phawng ding in, mipite mitmuh in,
 Kalvari tangah a khaikang ui.

[V5]
 4. Thimin A mel a lieh suongpi cheng le a khii,
 Lungdawnna aw thangviel a zak un;
 I Lalpau aw ahi, thihna huoisie thuokin,
 I bawna gitloh ngaihdam na di'n.

[V6]
 5. Amah a nuihsan ui, A thihding kuon chanin,
 A guolte lungkhamin a kap ui;
 Amah a taihsan ui, nat tincheng in a bawm,
 Mahleh tang achun a taihsan ui.

[V7]
 6. Nisa'n a en ngam puoi, lei le a kiling hi,
 A siempau a khetden tak ziekun;
 Ngai un, thihna apat, Belam No mawhpuopa,
 Than sung apat Tho kitin A hung.</lyrics>
<title>THERE IS A HILL</title>
<hymn_number>126</hymn_number>
</song>